                            <td class="text-nowrap">Licenca comercial<a href="https://www.nocobase.com/pt/agreement" target="_blank" class="text-muted" data-bs-toggle="tooltip" data-bs-placement="top" title="Ver detalhes"> <i class="fea icon-ex-md me-2 mt-1 uil uil-external-link-alt"></i></a></td>
